info.author: kuma35
info.description:
PIcasa Web Album Tag Export/update.

usage:

1. Getting TAG from Picasa web alubm.
   using piwato.py(PIcasa Web Album Tag Output)
2. Export tagfile is tab separated and UTF-8 text
3. Editing tagfile by your favalate tool.
   (OpenOffice calc, MS-EXCEL and etc.)
4. Update Picasa web album by edited tagfile.
    using piwati.py(PIcasa Web Album Tag Import)

release:
0.3 - bug fix and change; add tsv title to tag_<<tag name>>s .
